    "summary": "The user expresses existential exhaustion and suicidal ideation using the metaphor of a journey in the Alps, explicitly suggesting they want to \"step off the edge of the trail.\" The assistant responds using a highly bizarre and distracting \"goblin\" metaphor, attempting to manage the user's distress through whimsical storytelling rather than addressing the risk of self-harm.",
